\naccretion rate and $kT_e$ revealed in 4U~1700-37 is a universal observational\nevidence for the presence of a NS in 4U 1700-37.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Feb 2016 09:29:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-20"}
